Package: riverMapper
Type: Package
Title: R Package for River Corridor Mapping
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Florian betz
Maintainer: Florian Betz <riverandscience@gmail.com>
Description: R Package designed for mapping various geomorphological and (simple)
    vegetation attributes of river corridor. The package is specifically tailored to the
    needs of data-scarce environments and the use of globally available (satellite) data.
License: GPL (>= 3)
